body [arg]: See the body of a player
invite: Invite the bot to your server
male <thing> [member]: Use this when someone says that a thing is a female but is a male
female <thing> [member]: Use this when someone says that a thing is a male but is a female
codeblock <language> <code>: Transform a code to a codeblock
messages [limit=500] [channel] [member]:
See how many messages a member sent in a channel in the last tot messages
Use `messages <limit> <channel> <member>`
spoiler <message>: Make a message with a lot of spoilers
timezone [timezone]: See what time is in a country
satoru: See a random image of Satoru Fujinuma
kayo: See a random image of Kayo Hinazuki
autotrigger <trigger>: See a response giving a trigger
translate <text> [source] [destination]: Translate a phrase in every language. Use - e?translate "your text here" first_language second_language - Write languages as en, it, es, fr....
feedback <feedback>: Send a feedback to the bot or suggest a new command
head [arg]: See the head of a player
helm [arg]: See the head of a player with the helm (if there is)
cubehead [arg]: See the head of a player in a 3D way
bust [arg]: See the bust of a player
